<ul>
<li>Terms finalization and offer preparation</li>
<li>Agreement signing (office visit or mobile service)</li>
<li>Same-day or next-day disbursement</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Why the Speed Difference?</strong></p>
<p>Banks are slower because:</p>
<ul>
<li>Regulatory compliance requirements</li>
<li>Multiple approval layers</li>
<li>Comprehensive risk assessment</li>
<li>Standardized processes with limited flexibility</li>
<li>Higher volume processing systems</li>
</ul>
<p>Non-banks are faster because:</p>
<ul>
<li>Simplified approval workflows</li>
<li>Decision-maker accessibility</li>
<li>Risk-based pricing models</li>
<li>Flexible evaluation criteria</li>
<li>Focus on speed as competitive advantage</li>
